title: VA Indie Pop Rock Playlists July 2013 (Dutch Treat HQ)
description:
Simply the `best` 244 Indie tracks, I could find, from last month. Arranged according to sound quality, speed, volume and type of music into seven playlists. An eighth one (I9=unsorted) is added containing those tracks that made it through the sound barrier but did not make it into the playlists (for whatever reason).... Enjoy,

(PS Specs are a bit strange. First directory does not show. Please report any problems)

~@~ Indie 1307

I1 Breeze (Easy Pop)
I2 Bright Smile (Pop)
I2 Fantasy
I2 Follow Follow (Electro Pop Rock)
I3 Into The Sun (Electro Rock)
I3 Space (Electro Rock)
I4 Rootless (Solid Rock)
I9 Muzik (Divers Unsorted)
